{
  "stem": "7093.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he handed it in to-- to Vienna to the Freud Museum-- is where Freud wrote that he doesn't know much about music.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But he did print his essay on the psychology of music.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this essay is up to-- up there today being quoted by anyone who writes about-- deals with the psychology of music.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, there are an American publication which came out a couple of years ago, a French publication which came out a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And again and again and again, his name still crops up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He played the violin and the viola.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother played the piano.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think that she was considered not very good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- my brother was extremely gifted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He sang, supposedly sang Haydn symphonies before he even spoke.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was altogether very bright.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he became a professional pianist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and I was-- I was singing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could sing from any-- any music that was put in front of me from the age of nine.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And through my life, I used my knowledge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had a pretty decent voice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Unfortunately, now it's practically gone, which is very sad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But-- I had-- I-- I-- later on I sang in choirs and in important choirs, like the Philharmonia Choir here in its best days, in its top days.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Or-- and whenever I was hungry, then I sang in synagogue choirs or radio choirs or wherever they paid me a bad fee.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I needed the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I sang.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But coming back to it, as I said my, father played.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I-- I learned to play the cello.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As a youngster, I hated it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But eventually, I quite liked it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I didn't-- never had proper tuition.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because in town, there was no teacher.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
